      updatedAt

        paymentType
        published
        requirements

          jobId
          status

mutation UpdateClient($input: UpdateClientInput!) {
  updateClient(input: $input) {
    success
    message
    result {
      id
      companyName
      ceoFirstName
      ceoLastName
      jobTitle
      companyEmail
      companyPhone
      companyAddress
      postalCode
      registrationNumber
      website
      companyLocation
      verificationStatus
      dateJoined
    }
  }
}

      companyEmail
      companyPhone
      companyAddress
      companyLocation
      companyLogo
      ceoFirstName
      ceoLastName
      jobTitle
      postalCode

      website
      linkedIn
      locationCoordinates
    }
  }
}
